Text: LIVE CONCERT WITH THE HIVES! Stockholm, Cirkus Aug 26 2004. One whole hour with The Hives in full action! If you are a fan, you don't wan't to miss this! (Some swedish speaking in intruduktion.) The winners of the Gold Price Group of the year, The Golden Microfone Price, Swedish Grammy Award of Music of the Swedish Radio, and so on,so on! ThanX for the U.L!
